Compilation And Installation 
*****************************

1. Install build dependencies
     
    Debian-based
    -------------
    * g++ >= 5
    * libx11-dev and libxext-dev
    * qtbase5-dev and libqt5x11extras5-dev
    * libqt5svg5-dev 
    * qttools5-dev-tools

    Red Hat based
    --------------
    * gcc-c++
    * libX11-devel
    * libXext-devel
    * qt5-qtx11extras-devel
    * qt5-qtbase-devel
    * qt5-qtsvg-devel
    * qt5-qttools-devel

    Arch based
    ------------
    * gcc 
    * libx11 and libxext
    * qt5-base and qt5-x11extras
    * qt5-svg 
    * qt5-tools

    OpenSUSE based
    ---------------
    * gcc-c++
    * libX11-devel
    * libXext-devel
    * libqt5-qtx11extras-devel
    * libqt5-qtbase-devel
    * libqt5-qtsvg-devel
    * libqt5-qttools-devel

2. Building and installation

    * qmake  <PATH of QuickStitch.pro>
    * make 
    * sudo make install

